The paper focuses on incorporating external knowledge into machine reading for generative question answering, which involves natural language processing, artificial intelligence, and machine learning. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (IR) and neural networks (NE), which are also relevant sub-categories.
